title: The most explored glaciers by the number of expeditions
summary: The chart shows the most explored Glacier in relation to the Number of expeditions conducted .
The Mefonna has had the largest Number of expeditions by far with over 12 while Tasman has had only 2 .
Akkem has had a little over 8 while Zvezda has had 6 and Olav has seen a little over 4 expeditions .
gold: The chart shows the most explored glaciers based on the number of expeditions to each glacier \n\\n Chart shows most popular is the Mefonna glacier with the least popular being the Tasman . Akkem , Zvezda and Olav are in the middle range .
